Package: lissr
Title: View, Download, and Merge LISS Panel Data
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: person("Siard", "van den Bosch", email = "siardvandenbosch@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Programmatic access to the LISS Data Archive
    (<https://www.lissdata.nl/>). Authenticate with two-factor
    verification, browse available modules and waves, interactively
    select and download data files, and merge longitudinal waves using
    recipe-driven YAML specifications conforming to a canonical schema
    (v1.0.0), with a rule-driven income-cleaning framework producing
    audit-grade decision ledgers and reports. Credentials are stored
    securely via the system keyring.
